This product is a developer-assistant plugin for the x402 payment protocol.

It bundles documentation and protocol specifications from the x402 project for
local, search-based developer assistance:

  - .x402-specs/     — from x402 `specs/`
  - .x402-docs/      — from x402 `docs/`
  - .x402-sdk-docs/  — package READMEs from the x402 TypeScript and Python SDKs

That bundled material originates from the x402 project
(https://github.com/x402-foundation/x402), Copyright 2024 Coinbase, and is
licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0. The full Apache-2.0 license text
is included in LICENSE. The bundled documentation is unmodified except for being
copied into the .x402-*/ directories; SDK READMEs are renamed for clarity.

x402-pilot itself (the agent, commands, skills, conformance MCP, and scripts) is
original work by UIG Studios LLC, also offered under Apache-2.0.

To refresh the bundled corpus from upstream, run ./sync-specs.sh.
